## What "agent-based" means

This skill **orchestrates other marketplace skills** rather than calling external
APIs directly.  Sub-skills manage their own permissions.  This skill only needs
to declare `skill_dependencies` in its manifest.

## Installation

```bash
arcturus skill install {{ skill_name }}
```

